content:
Display FlexCard Data in a Tabular Structure

Add a Datatable to a FlexCard. Add the Datatable element in FlexCard Designer.

FlexCards Datatable Properties. Datatable element properties are configurable in the Property Panel when you select a Datatable element in the FlexCard Designer.

Download a Sample Datatable DataPack. Download a sample Datatable DataPack to import into your org.

A Datatable element lets you display a tabular structure of the data fetched from a data source on a FlexCard.
title: Displaying Tabular Data in FlexCards
